statements: SELECT * FROM SLA_Management;
SELECT SLA_ID, SLA_Type, Start_Date FROM SLA_Management WHERE Compliance_Status = TRUE;
SELECT Client_ID, Vendor_ID, SLA_Description, Start_Date, End_Date FROM SLA_Management WHERE SLA_Type = 'Gold';
SELECT SLA_ID, Vendor_ID, Compliance_Status FROM SLA_Management ORDER BY End_Date DESC;
SELECT Client_ID, SLA_Type, Compliance_Status FROM SLA_Management WHERE Start_Date >= '2022-01-01' AND End_Date <= '2022-06-30';
SELECT * FROM SLA_Management WHERE Client_ID = 10 ORDER BY End_Date DESC;
SELECT SLA_ID, SLA_Type, Compliance_Status FROM SLA_Management WHERE Vendor_ID = 5 AND Compliance_Status = true;
SELECT SLA_Description FROM SLA_Management WHERE SLA_Type LIKE 'Service%' ORDER BY SLA_ID ASC;
SELECT Client_ID, End_Date, SLA_Type FROM SLA_Management WHERE Compliance_Status = false AND Start_Date < '2022-12-31';
SELECT SLA_ID, Vendor_ID, Start_Date, End_Date FROM SLA_Management ORDER BY Start_Date ASC, Vendor_ID DESC;

SELECT v.vendor_name, c.client_name FROM Vendors v INNER JOIN Clients c ON v.vendor_id = c.client_id
SELECT c.client_name, s.agreed_service, s.end_date FROM Clients c INNER JOIN SLAs s ON c.client_id = s.client_id

SELECT c.client_name, v.vendor_name, co.status FROM Clients c INNER JOIN SLAs s ON c.client_id = s.client_id INNER JOIN Vendors v ON s.vendor_id = v.vendor_id INNER JOIN Compliance co ON s.sla_id = co.sla_id

SELECT c.client_name, v.vendor_name FROM Clients c INNER JOIN SLAs s ON c.client_id = s.client_id INNER JOIN Vendors v ON s.vendor_id = v.vendor_id
SELECT c.client_name, COUNT(s.sla_id) AS total_slas FROM Clients c LEFT JOIN SLAs s ON c.client_id = s.client_id GROUP BY c.client_name
